name: Ammu Demo Import
author: Ammuthemes

sections.description:
A plugin to install demo content to themes developed by Ammuthemes.
This plugin requires the One Click Demo Import plugin to be installed.

Supported Themes

  1. Real Estate Salient

sections.installation:
*** From your WordPress dashboard ***

  1. Visit ‘Plugins > Add New’,
  2. Search for ‘Ammu Demo Import’ and install the plugin.
  3. Activate ‘Ammu Demo Import’ from your Plugins page.
sections.faq:
Does this plugin works with any WordPress theme

No, This plugin will only work with the themes developed by Ponvendhan.
